            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>竣邦-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4442:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4442\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4442-TW</a>)14日12:20股價上漲4.6元，報59.4元，漲幅8.39%，成交205張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>竣邦-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4442:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4442\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4442-TW</a>)所屬產業為紡織纖維，主要業務為成衣服裝機能性布料之開發、設計、生產及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌3.18%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.69%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-21 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-14 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-7 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
